latestPosts.caption:
we had such a fun time this week staying at @thisisdreamscape’s salt key property! 🌴🌞

some of our favorite things about this place:

• The beach is literally right next to the house - just steps away! 
• The big pool out back — we spent soooo much time here
• Tons of space! It was just me + my parents this time, but it sleeps up to 10 comfortably 
• The grill, surrounded by palm trees and perfect for outdoor cookouts by the pool
• Bikes that were perfect for quick food runs + exploring
